      Case Information and Privacy Release Form
           In order for Congressman Carson to assist you, it is necessary
      that you provide all the information requested below. Please print out
      the CASE INFORMATION AND PRIVACY RELEASE FORM, complete it, sign it,
      and mail it to the address listed below.
      Congressman Brad Carson
      Attention: Casework
      215 State Street, Suite 815
      Muskogee, Oklahoma 74401
